Install DosBox on Debian
apt install dosbox

Download games (zip files)
http://www.abandonia.com/en/game/all?page=3
https://www.dosgamesarchive.com/


In linux create a folder in / like dosbox
cd / && mkdir dosbox
PS: You might need to apply chmod +x /dosbox

in linux extract downloaded game zip to /dosbox

Switch on dosbox 
$ dosbox

In dosbox mount the linux folder : 
z:\>mount c /dosbox
You get a message of sucessfull mount

Then you step into c using dos synthax 
c:

You browse c as in dos : 
c:\>dir

Navigate to the game subdir (if present) , and you just run the game exe file.


